                  PERFORM S3200-FINAL-SAVE-RTN
                     THRU S3200-FINAL-SAVE-EXT
           WHEN CO-CHA-07
230330*           삭제처리
                  PERFORM S3300-DELETE-RTN
                     THRU S3300-DELETE-EXT
           END-EVALUATE

           .
       S3000-PROCESS-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  THKJL0005 협의위원 : 의견등록
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3100-ADD-OPIN-RTN.

      *@3.1 초기화
           INITIALIZE TKJL0005-KEY
                      TRJL0005-REC

      *@3.2 호출변수 MOVE
      *@  그룹회사코드
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO KJL0005-PK-GROUP-CO-CD
      *@  한도신청번호
           MOVE XDJL0B19-I-LIMT-APLCN-NO
             TO KJL0005-PK-LIMT-APLCN-NO
      *@  승인위원직원번호
           IF   XDJL0B19-I-PRCSS-DSTIC = CO-CHA-04
                MOVE BICOM-USER-EMPID
                  TO KJL0005-PK-ATHOR-CMMB-EMPID
           ELSE
                MOVE XDJL0B19-I-ATHOR-CMMB-EMPID
                  TO KJL0005-PK-ATHOR-CMMB-EMPID
           END-IF

      *@3.3 UPDATE전에LOCK SELECT검색
           #DYDBIO SELECT-CMD-Y TKJL0005-PK TRJL0005-REC

      *@3.4 호출결과　확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN COND-DBIO-OK
                    CONTINUE
           WHEN COND-DBIO-MRNF
      *        #CSTMSG CO-MSG5     CO-SUBMSG1
               #ERROR  CO-B2500200 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           WHEN OTHER
               #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE

      *@3.5 갱신변수 MOVE
           IF   XDJL0B19-I-PRCSS-DSTIC = CO-CHA-04
      *@        한도승인구분
                MOVE XDJL0B19-I-LIMT-ATHOR-DSTIC
                  TO RJL0005-LIMT-ATHOR-DSTCD
      *@        승인의견내용
                MOVE XDJL0B19-I-ATHOR-OPIN-CTNT
                  TO RJL0005-ATHOR-OPIN-CTNT
           ELSE
      *@        한도승인구분
                MOVE CO-CHA-5
                  TO RJL0005-LIMT-ATHOR-DSTCD
      *@        승인의견내용
                MOVE '불참'
                  TO RJL0005-ATHOR-OPIN-CTNT
           END-IF

      *@3.6 DBIO CALL
           #DYDBIO UPDATE-CMD-Y TKJL0005-PK TRJL0005-REC

      *@3.7 호출결과　확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN COND-DBIO-OK
231012*@       신청직원번호 검색
               PERFORM S3110-APLCN-EMPID-RTN
                  THRU S3110-APLCN-EMPID-EXT

231012*@       승인구분 체크
               PERFORM S3120-THKJL0005-CHK-RTN
                  THRU S3120-THKJL0005-CHK-EXT

               IF WK-CHK-YN = 'Y'
231012*@           메신저처리
                   PERFORM S3130-MESSENGER-SEND-RTN
                      THRU S3130-MESSENGER-SEND-EXT
               END-IF
           WHEN COND-DBIO-MRNF
      *        #CSTMSG CO-MSG5     CO-SUBMSG1
               #ERROR  CO-B2500200 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           WHEN OTHER
               #ERROR CO-B4200224 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE

           .
       S3100-ADD-OPIN-EXT.
           EXIT.
