       S3110-APLCN-EMPID-RTN.
      *@   초기화
           INITIALIZE TKJL0018-KEY
                      TRJL0018-REC

      *    그룹회사코드
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO KJL0018-PK-GROUP-CO-CD
      *    한도신청번호
           MOVE XDJL0B19-I-LIMT-APLCN-NO
