231012*@  승인구분 체크
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3120-THKJL0005-CHK-RTN.
      *@2.1변수초기화
           INITIALIZE TKJL0005-KEY
                      TRJL0005-REC
      *@2.2변수 MOVE
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO KJL0005-PK-GROUP-CO-CD
           MOVE XDJL0B19-I-LIMT-APLCN-NO
             TO KJL0005-PK-LIMT-APLCN-NO
           MOVE LOW-VALUE
             TO KJL0005-PK-ATHOR-CMMB-EMPID

           #DYDBIO  OPEN-CMD-1 TKJL0005-PK TRJL0005-REC

      *@1.1 조회결과확인
      *@처리내용 : IF 조회 error 이면 에러처리
           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN COND-DBIO-OK

               MOVE 'Y'
                 TO WK-CHK-YN

               PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WK-I > 100
                            OR COND-DBIO-MRNF

                   #DYDBIO  FETCH-CMD-1 TKJL0005-PK TRJL0005-REC

                   EVALUATE TRUE
                   WHEN COND-DBIO-OK

                       IF RJL0005-LIMT-ATHOR-DSTCD = CO-CHA-0
                           MOVE 'N'
                             TO WK-CHK-YN
                       END-IF
                   WHEN COND-DBIO-MRNF
                       CONTINUE
                   END-EVALUATE

               END-PERFORM
           WHEN COND-DBIO-MRNF
               CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
      *       원장에러일경우　에러처리
               #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3120-THKJL0005-CHK-EXT.
           EXIT.
