      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3130-MESSENGER-SEND-RTN.

      *@메신저처리
      *@   COPYBOOK 초기화
           INITIALIZE XZUGMSNM-IN

      *@유틸리티　파라미터 MOVE
      *@   서비스유형
           MOVE CO-CHA-0
             TO XZUGMSNM-IN-SERVTYPE

      *@   수신직원번호
           MOVE WK-APLCN-EMPID
             TO XZUGMSNM-IN-REMPNO

      *@   발신직원번호
           MOVE BICOM-USER-EMPID
             TO XZUGMSNM-IN-SENDNO

      *@   쪽지제목
           MOVE '포괄신용공여한도 적정성 점검 승인'
             TO XZUGMSNM-IN-TITLE

      *@   쪽지본문
           STRING '한도신청번호 : ' XDJL0B19-I-LIMT-APLCN-NO
                                                    DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  CO-CHAR-LF                        DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'KB-PIN : ' XDJL0B19-I-CUST-IDNFR DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  CO-CHAR-LF                        DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  '포괄신용공여한도 적정성점검 '
                  '승인이 완료되었습니다.'
                                                    DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  CO-CHAR-LF                        DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  '담당심사역은 최종확정 바랍니다.'
                                                    DELIMITED BY SIZE
             INTO XZUGMSNM-IN-BODY

      *@   긴급여부
           MOVE CO-CHA-1
             TO XZUGMSNM-IN-URGENTYN

      *@   발신함저장여부
           MOVE CO-CHA-1
             TO XZUGMSNM-IN-SAVEOPTION

      *@   UTILITY CALL
           #DYCALL ZUGMSNM YCCOMMON-CA XZUGMSNM-CA

      *@   유틸리티　처리결과　확인
           IF NOT COND-XZUGMSNM-OK
              #USRLOG '결과:' XZUGMSNM-R-STAT
           END-IF
           .
