      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3210-FINAL-CHK-RTN.
      *@2.1변수초기화
           INITIALIZE TKJL0005-KEY
                      TRJL0005-REC
      *@2.2변수 MOVE
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO KJL0005-PK-GROUP-CO-CD
           MOVE XDJL0B19-I-LIMT-APLCN-NO
             TO KJL0005-PK-LIMT-APLCN-NO
           MOVE LOW-VALUE
             TO KJL0005-PK-ATHOR-CMMB-EMPID

           #DYDBIO  OPEN-CMD-1 TKJL0005-PK TRJL0005-REC

      *@1.1 조회결과확인
      *@처리내용 : IF 조회 error 이면 에러처리
