           WHEN COND-DBIO-OK

               MOVE 'Y'
                 TO WK-FINAL-CHK-YN

               PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WK-I > 100
                            OR COND-DBIO-MRNF

